doctype html
html
  head
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='navbar.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', type='text/css', href='stylesheets/bootstrap.min.css')
    title Contact Us
  body(style='background-color: #424242; color: #FFFFFF')
    nav.navbar.navbar-inverse
      .container-fluid
        .navbar-header
          a(href='/main')
            img(src='images/BBS_logo2-4.png')
        div
          br
          a(href='/profile')
            .text(style='float: right; margin-top: 50px; font-size: 20px; color: #0B614B')
              b Maheen
            form.navbar-form.pull-right
              .dropdown
                a.dropdown-toggle(href='#', style='color:#FFFFFF; font-size:50px; float: right;', data-toggle='dropdown', role='button', aria-haspopup='true', aria-expanded='false')
                  | ? 
                  span.caret
                ul.dropdown-menu
                  li
                    a(href='') About Us 
                  li
                    a(href='') Contact Us
                  li
                    a(href='/logout') Log Out
            span
              a(href='/community')
                img#globe(align='right', src='images/globe.png')
    .row
      br
      .col-md-8.col-sm-8
        br
        center
          h1(style='margin-top: 1px') Contact Us
        div
          br
          p(style='margin-left: 20px; font-size: 20px;')
            | Please use the form below to get in touch with us. In the case of complaints and/or corporate enquiries, please provide as much information as possible, so we can address your query accordingly.
          section(style='margin-left: 90px')
            form#name.form-horizontal(role = 'form',method='post', name='message', action='/contact_us/submit')
              br
              .form-group
                label.control-label.col-sm-3
                  | Name:
                  span.text-danger
                .col-md-15.col-sm-9
                  .input-group
                    input#name.form-control(type='text', name='name', placeholder='Enter your name', value='')
              br
              .form-group
                label.control-label.col-sm-3
                  | Email address:
                  span.text-danger
                .col-md-15.col-sm-9
                  .input-group
                    input#email.form-control(type='email', name='email', placeholder='Enter your email address', value='')
              br
              .form-group
                label.control-label.col-sm-3
                  | Phone number:
                  span.text-danger
                .col-md-15.col-sm-9
                  .input-group
                    input#phone.form-control(type='tel', name='phone', placeholder='Enter your number', value='')
              br
              .form-group
                label.control-label.col-sm-3
                  | Type:
                  span.text-danger
                .col-xs-8
                  .form-inline
                    select.form-control(name='type')
                      option(value='Complaint') Complaint 
                      option(value='Feedback') Feedback 
                      option(value='General Inquiry') General Inquiry 
              br
              .form-group
                label.control-label.col-sm-3
                  | Message:
                  span.text-danger
                .col-md-15.col-sm-9
                  .input-group
                    input#message.form-control(type='text',name='message', placeholder='Enter your message', value='')
              br
              br
              .form-group
                div(style='margin-left:250px ')
                  input.btn.btn-primary(name='Submit', type='submit', value='Submit')
      .col-md-3.col-sm-3
        center
          h1  About Us 
        br
        center
          p(style='font-size: 20px')
            | BBS is a platform designed to connect buyers and sellers from the LUMS community. With BBS, you can buy, borrow and sell anything that exists in the world (well, within the LUMS community). They can range from mobile phones to calculators to sleeping bags. Once you have selected a product you want to buy, use the contact information available on the ad to contact the seller. 
            br
          p(style='font-size: 25px')
            | BBS. Simple. Hassle-free. No Yaind.
          br
          br
          p
            | Note: BBS is not responsible for any damaged goods. No monetary transactions can be carried out using the website.
    script(src='https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.12.4/jquery.min.js')
    script(src='javascripts/bootstrap.min.js')

